OL,3,CBurnley head coach exits after club's
OL,4,Crelegation
OL,6,FScott Parker has left Burnley by
OL,7,Fmutual consent, just eight days after
OL,8,Fthe club's relegation from the Premier
OL,9,FLeague.
OL,11,FParker, who took charge in July 2024
OL,12,Fand signed a three-year contract, led
OL,13,Fthe Clarets back to the top flight
OL,14,Flast season with a second-place
OL,15,FChampionship finish.
OL,17,FHowever, this campaign has been a
OL,18,Fstruggle, with Burnley winning only
OL,19,Ffour of their 34 league games and
OL,20,Fpicking up just one point from their
OL,21,Flast eight matches.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
