OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777546976
OL,3,CBurnley head coach exits after club's
OL,4,Crelegation
OL,6,FBurnley won three of their first nine
OL,7,Fleague matches this season, but losing
OL,8,Ftheir next seven meant they plunged
OL,9,Finto the relegation zone.
OL,11,FPark said: "It has been an immense
OL,12,Fprivilege to lead this great club over
OL,13,Fthe past two years. I have enjoyed
OL,14,Fevery moment of our journey together,
OL,15,Fbut feel that now is the right time
OL,16,Ffor both parties to move in a
OL,17,Fdifferent direction.
OL,26,@sD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
