CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777546976
OL,3,CBurnley head coach exits after club's
OL,4,Crelegation
OL,6,FI reflect back with great pride on
OL,7,Fwhat we achieved during my time at the
OL,8,Fclub, especially our unforgettable
OL,9,Fpromotion season in 2024/25, and it
OL,10,Fwas a true honour to lead this team
OL,11,Finto the Premier League."
OL,13,FParker came into the club after the
OL,14,Fdeparture of Vincent Kompany before
OL,15,Fthe 2024-25 season.
OL,17,FIn his farewell message, Parker said:
OL,18,F"I would like to thank Alan and the
OL,19,Fownership group for their support
OL,20,Fduring my time at the club.
OL,26,@sD@YO]
