PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777546976
OL,3,CBurnley head coach exits after club's
OL,4,Crelegation
OL,6,F"My thanks also go to the fantastic
OL,7,Fand tireless staff behind the scenes
OL,8,Fand, most importantly, to the players,
OL,9,Fwho have given me everything since the
OL,10,Ffirst day I arrived.
OL,12,F"Finally, thank you to the Burnley
OL,13,Ffans. I wish you all and this great
OL,14,Fclub nothing but the very best for the
OL,15,Ffuture."
OL,17,FAssistant coach Mike Jackson will take
OL,18,Fcharge of Burnley for the final four
OL,19,Fgames of the season, starting with
OL,20,FFriday's trip to Leeds United.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
